# Lanka Auto Price Tracker (Chrome Extension)

A lightweight Google Chrome extension built with Manifest V3 that dynamically tracks and logs vehicle price histories across major Sri Lankan automobile marketplaces.

## Features
- **Multi-platform Support:** Works seamlessly on Ikman.lk, Riyasewana.com, Patpat.lk, and Autolanka.com.
- **Dynamic Price Scraping:** Automatically detects and extracts titles and listing prices.
- **Real-time Price History:** Fetches and stores updates using a Firebase Realtime Database backend.
- **Interactive UI:** Injects a sleek, dark-mode-ready floating card overlay on product pages, and features an extension toolbar popup.

## Tech Stack
- JavaScript (DOM Manipulation, Chrome Extension API)
- HTML5 & CSS3 (Custom responsive UI components)
- Firebase Realtime Database